PRIVACY POLICY
This privacy policy governs your use of all software applications for mobile devices that were created by IMAPPS. These applications include pranks, games, and utility tools.
What information does the Application obtain and how is it used?
User Provided Information
Our Applications do not obtain any information provided by you during download, as no registration or login is required. Audio recording permission is used for sound level interaction but isn't saved or stored.
Automatically Collected Information
Our Applications may collect certain information automatically, including device type, unique ID, IP address, mobile OS, and usage patterns.
Location Information
The Application does not collect precise real-time location data.
Third Party Access
We may share information with third parties as described in this privacy statement, including legal obligations, safety concerns, and trusted service providers.
Automatic Data Collection and Advertising
We work with analytics and advertising networks for app usage and anonymous targeted advertising purposes.
Opt-out Rights
You can stop information collection by uninstalling the Application.
Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated, and continued use is deemed approval of changes.
Your Consent
By using the Application, you consent to the processing of your information as outlined in this Privacy Policy.
Contact Us
If you have privacy questions, contact us at inigo333@gmail.com.